                                "stop": 10.975,
                                "byte_start": 87552,
                                "byte_stop": 131542,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court number 94-5707, Wilson against Arkansas will be announced by Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
